Third-party notice

This resource is a vehicle spawner menu for FiveM. It does not include or
distribute GabZ vehicle models, textures, or other assets.

A valid GabZ vehicle pack license is required to use this spawner with the
referenced vehicles. The GabZ vehicle pack is a separate commercial product
and must be purchased independently:

- GabZ: https://fivem.gabzv.com
- GabZ Vehicle Pack (required): https://fivem.gabzv.com/package/6108207

Vehicle spawn codes and metadata used in this project are sourced from the
GabZ Vehicle Data community repository:

- https://github.com/JustBlueDolphin/Gabz-Vehicle-Data

Thank you to JustBlueDolphin for providing and maintaining this data. That
repository is a separate community project and is not affiliated with GabZ
or this spawner resource.

The spawn codes and metadata only work when the official GabZ vehicle pack
is installed and properly licensed on your server.

This project is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by GabZ or
JustBlueDolphin.